#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "IA2"
msgid_plural "IA2s"
msgstr[0] "IA2"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The IA2 is a select fire assault rifle designed to replace the aging FAL, "
"M16 A2, and HK33's that are in service with the brazilian military . It's "
"covered in picatany rails and can support a wide range of attachments. The "
"standard length assault rifle variant has a 17.2 inch barrel (440mm) and "
"accepts any STANAG pattern magazines."
msgstr ""
"IA2是一款可選射擊模式的突擊步槍，旨在取代巴西軍隊中老舊的FAL、M16 "
"A2和HK33。它覆蓋有皮卡汀尼導軌，可支持多種附件。標準長度的突擊步槍型號擁有17.2英寸（440毫米）槍管，並能兼容任何STANAG規格的彈匣。"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\308.json .\gun\7.92x33k.json .\gun\762.json
