#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "IA2 CQC"
msgid_plural "IA2 CQCs"
msgstr[0] "IA2 CQC"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The IA2 is a select fire assault rifle designed to replace the aging FAL, "
"M16 A2, and HK33's that are in service with the brazilian military . It's "
"covered in picatany rails and can support a wide range of attachments. The "
"CQC variant has a 10.3 inch barrel (260mm) and accepts any STANAG pattern "
"magazines."
msgstr ""
"IA2是一款可選射擊模式的突擊步槍，旨在取代巴西軍隊中老舊的FAL、M16 "
"A2和HK33。它覆蓋有皮卡汀尼導軌，可支持多種附件。CQC型號擁有10.3英寸（260毫米）槍管，並能兼容任何STANAG規格的彈匣。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "IA2 Carbine"
msgid_plural "IA2 Carbines"
msgstr[0] "IA2卡賓槍"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The IA2 carbine is a select fire assault rifle designed to replace the aging"
" FAL, M16 A2, and HK33's that are in service with the brazilian military . "
"It's covered in picatany rails and can support a wide range of attachments. "
"The carbine variant has a 14.5 inch barrel (370mm) and accepts any STANAG "
"pattern magazines."
msgstr ""
"IA2卡賓槍是一款可選射擊模式的突擊步槍，旨在取代巴西軍隊中老舊的FAL、M16 "
"A2和HK33。它覆蓋有皮卡汀尼導軌，可支持多種附件。卡賓槍型號擁有14.5英寸（370毫米）槍管，並能兼容任何STANAG規格的彈匣。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "RDB"
msgid_plural "RDBs"
msgstr[0] "RDB"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"Unlike traditional bullpups, the RDB ejects the brass downwards out of the "
"weapon, making the RDB is on of the few truly ambidexterous firearms on the "
"market"
msgstr "與傳統無託式步槍不同，RDB將彈殼向下拋出槍外，使其成為市場上少數真正左右手通用的槍械之一。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "M-231"
msgid_plural "M-231s"
msgstr[0] "M-231"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The m231 port firing weapon is a heavily modified M16 pattern rifle. It has "
"no stock, no sights, a threaded hand guard to screw into the firing ports on"
" US military armored vehicles, and a lucidcrously high rate of fire. It was "
"never intened to leave the vehicle it was issued with."
msgstr ""
"M-231射擊孔武器是一款經過大幅改裝的M16型步槍。它沒有槍托和瞄具，配有螺紋護木以旋入美軍裝甲車輛的射擊孔，並擁有極高的射速。它從未被設計用於離開其配屬的車輛。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "full auto"
msgstr "全自動"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "XM-231"
msgid_plural "XM-231s"
msgstr[0] "XM-231"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The xm231 port firing weapon is a heavily modified M16 pattern rifle. unlike"
" the m231 the mx231 has a wire collapsing stock and rudamentary sights, but "
"it still has the threaded hand guard to screw into the firing ports on US "
"military armored vehicles, and a lucidcrously high rate of fire. It was "
"never intened to leave the vehicle it was issued with."
msgstr ""
"XM-231射擊孔武器是一款經過大幅改裝的M16型步槍。與M-231不同，XM-231配有鋼絲摺疊槍托和基礎瞄具，但仍保留螺紋護木以旋入美軍裝甲車輛的射擊孔，並擁有極高的射速。它從未被設計用於離開其配屬的車輛。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "XM-29 OICW"
msgid_plural "XM-29 OICWs"
msgstr[0] "XM-29 OICW"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The XM-29 OICW is an expirimental rifle that was intended to replace the "
"M-16 rifles currently in service with the US military. The OICW is a "
"Selectable Assault Battle Rifle that consists of two parts. a 20x28mm HE "
"module with a barrel length of 460 mm and a modified G36 with a barrel "
"length of 250 mm. Despite increasing the available firepower of any given "
"soldier it's insanely heavy and isn't great at engaging targets at longer "
"ranges."
msgstr ""
"XM-29 "
"OICW是一款實驗性步槍，旨在取代美軍現役的M-16步槍。OICW是一款可選射擊模式的突擊戰鬥步槍，由兩部分組成：一個槍管長460毫米的20x28毫米高爆模塊，以及一個槍管長250毫米的改進型G36。儘管它能提升單兵火力，但其重量極大，且在遠距離交戰中表現不佳。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a1"
msgid_plural "M16a1s"
msgstr[0] "M16a1"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The first generation of the M16. Introduced in vietnam as a replacement for "
"the m14 this rifle suffered from many mechanical failures and was over all a"
" very poor weapon."
msgstr "M16的第一代型號。在越南戰爭中作為M14的替代品引入，這款步槍存在許多機械故障，總體而言是一款非常糟糕的武器。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "m16a1 (semi-auto)"
msgid_plural "m16a1 (semi-auto)s"
msgstr[0] "M16a1（半自動）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The first generation of the M16. Introduced in vietnam as a replacement for "
"the m14 this rifle suffered from many mechanical failures and was over all a"
" very poor weapon. This rifle is a civilian reproduction."
msgstr "M16的第一代型號。在越南戰爭中作為M14的替代品引入，這款步槍存在許多機械故障，總體而言是一款非常糟糕的武器。此步槍為民用復刻版。"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a1 (burst)"
msgid_plural "M16a1 (burst)s"
msgstr[0] "M16a1（點射）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The first generation of the M16. Introduced in vietnam as a replacement for "
"the m14 this rifle suffered from many mechanical failures and was over all a"
" very poor weapon. This rifle has an a2 lower receiver giving it burst fire "
"capabilities instead of full-auto."
msgstr ""
"M16的第一代型號。在越南戰爭中作為M14的替代品引入，這款步槍存在許多機械故障，總體而言是一款非常糟糕的武器。此步槍採用A2下機匣，使其具備點射功能而非全自動。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "burst"
msgstr "連發"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a1 (auto/burst)"
msgid_plural "M16a1 (auto/burst)s"
msgstr[0] "M16a1（全自動/點射）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The first generation of the M16. Introduced in vietnam as a replacement for "
"the m14 this rifle suffered from many mechanical failures and was over all a"
" very poor weapon. This rifle has an a3 lower receiver giving it burst fire "
"and full-auto capabilities."
msgstr ""
"M16的第一代型號。作為M14的替代品在越南戰爭中引入，這款步槍存在許多機械故障，總體而言是一款非常糟糕的武器。該步槍採用A3下機匣，具備點射和全自動射擊能力。"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\7.92x33k.json .\gun\9mm.json
msgid "full-auto"
msgstr "全自動"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a2"
msgid_plural "M16a2s"
msgstr[0] "M16a2"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The second generation of the M16. Full-auto was phased out in favor of a 3 "
"shot burst mode."
msgstr "M16的第二代型號。全自動模式被淘汰，改為三發點射模式。"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a2 (semi-auto)"
msgid_plural "M16a2 (semi-auto)s"
msgstr[0] "M16a2（半自動）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The second generation of the M16. This rifle is a civilian variant, as such "
"it only has semi-auto capabilities."
msgstr "M16的第二代型號。這款步槍為民用版本，因此僅具備半自動射擊能力。"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a2 (auto)"
msgid_plural "M16a2 (auto)s"
msgstr[0] "M16a2（全自動）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The second generation of the M16. This rifle has an a1 lower reciver giving "
"full-auto capabilities instead of 3 shot burst."
msgstr "M16的第二代型號。這款步槍採用A1下機匣，具備全自動射擊能力，而非三發點射。"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a2 (auto/burst)"
msgid_plural "M16a2 (auto/burst)s"
msgstr[0] "M16a2（全自動/點射）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The second generation of the M16. This rifle has an a3 lower reciver giving "
"full-auto and 3 shot burst capabilities."
msgstr "M16的第二代型號。這款步槍採用A3下機匣，具備全自動和三發點射能力。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "m16a3"
msgid_plural "m16a3s"
msgstr[0] "m16a3"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"the third generation of the M16 series of rifles. The a3 variants have an "
"intigrated quad-rail and a detachable carry handle for mounting optics, as "
"well as semi-auto, burst, and full-auto fire modes."
msgstr "M16系列步槍的第三代型號。A3變體配備一體化四導軌和可拆卸提把，用於安裝光學瞄具，並具備半自動、點射和全自動射擊模式。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "m16a3 (auto)"
msgid_plural "m16a3 (auto)s"
msgstr[0] "m16a3（全自動）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"the third generation of the M16 series of rifles. The a3 variants have an "
"intigrated quad-rail and a detachable carry handle for mounting optics. This"
" rifle has an a1 lower receiver and as such only has semi-auto and full-auto"
" capabilities."
msgstr ""
"M16系列步槍的第三代型號。A3變體配備一體化四導軌和可拆卸提把，用於安裝光學瞄具。該步槍採用A1下機匣，因此僅具備半自動和全自動射擊能力。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "m16a3 (burst)"
msgid_plural "m16a3 (burst)s"
msgstr[0] "m16a3（點射）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"the third generation of the M16 series of rifles. The a3 variants have an "
"intigrated quad-rail and a detachable carry handle for mounting optics. This"
" rifle has an a2 lower receiver and as such only has semi-auto and burst "
"capabilities."
msgstr "M16系列步槍的第三代型號。A3變體配備一體化四導軌和可拆卸提把，用於安裝光學瞄具。該步槍採用A2下機匣，因此僅具備半自動和點射能力。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "STG-44 (5.56x45)"
msgid_plural "STG-44 (5.56x45)s"
msgstr[0] "STG-44（5.56x45）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"widely considered to be one of the first assault rifles, the STG-44 was "
"produced in germany during the second world war and originally fired a "
"proprietary 7.92x33 kurtz round. This however is a reproduction rifle "
"chambered in a the more common 5.56x45 round."
msgstr ""
"被廣泛認為是首批突擊步槍之一，STG-44在第二次世界大戰期間於德國生產，最初發射專用的7.92x33 "
"Kurz彈藥。然而，這是一款復刻步槍，改用了更常見的5.56x45彈藥。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "STG-44 (5.56x45 SBR)"
msgid_plural "STG-44 (5.56x45 SBR)s"
msgstr[0] "STG-44（5.56x45 SBR）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"widely considered to be one of the first assault rifles, the STG-44 was "
"produced in germany during the second world war and originally fired a "
"proprietary 7.92x33 kurtz round. This however is a reproduction rifle "
"chambered in a the more common 5.56x45 round. It has also been cut down and "
"converted into an SBR"
msgstr ""
"被廣泛認為是首批突擊步槍之一，STG-44在第二次世界大戰期間於德國生產，最初發射專用的7.92x33 "
"Kurz彈藥。然而，這是一款復刻步槍，改用了更常見的5.56x45彈藥，並經過截短改裝為短管步槍（SBR）。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "STG-44 (5.56x45 pistol)"
msgid_plural "STG-44 (5.56x45 pistol)s"
msgstr[0] "STG-44（5.56x45 手槍型）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"widely considered to be one of the first assault rifles, the STG-44 was "
"produced in germany during the second world war and originally fired a "
"proprietary 7.92x33 kurtz round. This however is a reproduction rifle "
"chambered in a the more common 5.56x45 round. The stock has been cut off and"
" barrel sawed down to make for a very compact firearm."
msgstr ""
"被廣泛認為是首批突擊步槍之一，STG-44在第二次世界大戰期間於德國生產，最初發射專用的7.92x33 "
"Kurz彈藥。然而，這是一款復刻步槍，改用了更常見的5.56x45彈藥。槍托被切除，槍管鋸短，製成了一款非常緊湊的槍械。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "STG-44 (5.56x45 full-auto)"
msgid_plural "STG-44 (5.56x45 full-auto)s"
msgstr[0] "STG-44（5.56x45 全自動）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"widely considered to be one of the first assault rifles, the STG-44 was "
"produced in germany during the second world war and originally fired a "
"proprietary 7.92x33 kurtz round. This however is a reproduction rifle "
"chambered in a the more common 5.56x45 round. The lower receiver has been "
"replaced with an original lower receiver."
msgstr ""
"被廣泛認為是首批突擊步槍之一，STG-44在第二次世界大戰期間於德國生產，最初發射專用的7.92x33 "
"Kurz彈藥。然而，這是一款復刻步槍，改用了更常見的5.56x45彈藥。下機匣已更換為原裝下機匣。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "STG-44 (5.56x45 SBR full-auto)"
msgid_plural "STG-44 (5.56x45 SBR full-auto)s"
msgstr[0] "STG-44（5.56x45 SBR 全自動）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"widely considered to be one of the first assault rifles, the STG-44 was "
"produced in germany during the second world war and originally fired a "
"proprietary 7.92x33 kurtz round. This however is a reproduction rifle "
"chambered in a the more common 5.56x45 round. The lower receiver has been "
"replaced with an original lower receiver and it has also been cut down and "
"converted into an SBR."
msgstr ""
"被廣泛認為是首批突擊步槍之一，STG-44在第二次世界大戰期間於德國生產，最初發射專用的7.92x33 "
"Kurz彈藥。然而，這是一款復刻步槍，改用了更常見的5.56x45彈藥。下機匣已更換為原裝下機匣，並經過截短改裝為短管步槍（SBR）。"

