msgid_plural "STG-44 (5.56x45 pistol full-auto)s"
msgstr[0] "STG-44（5.56x45 手槍型 全自動）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"widely considered to be one of the first assault rifles, the STG-44 was "
"produced in germany during the second world war and originally fired a "
