#: .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a3"
msgid_plural "M16a3s"
msgstr[0] "M16a3"

#: .\gun\300blk.json
msgid ""
"the third generation of the M16 series of rifles. The a3 variants have an "
"intigrated quad-rail and a detachable carry handle for mounting optics, as "
"well as semi-auto, burst, and full-auto fire modes. This rifle is chambered "
"in 300 blackout"
msgstr ""
"M16系列步槍的第三代型號。A3變體配備一體化四導軌和可拆卸提把，用於安裝光學瞄具，並具備半自動、點射和全自動射擊模式。該步槍使用.300 "
"Blackout彈藥。"

