#: .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "ar-15"
msgid_plural "ar-15s"
msgstr[0] "ar-15"

#: .\gun\300blk.json
msgid ""
"This ubiquitous rifle is the forefather of M16 rifle series.  It is "
"lightweight and accurate, but will malfunction if not properly maintained.  "
"This one is a semi automatic civilian version and is chambered in 300 "
"blackout"
msgstr "這款普及型步槍是M16系列的前身。它輕便且精準，但若維護不當會發生故障。此為半自動民用版本，使用300 BLK口徑。"

#: .\gun\300blk.json
msgid ""
"The first generation of the M16. Introduced in vietnam as a replacement for "
"the m14 this rifle suffered from many mechanical failures and was over all a"
" very poor weapon. This rifle is chambered in 300 blackout"
msgstr "M16的第一代型號。在越南戰爭中作為M14的替代品引入，此步槍存在諸多機械故障，總體而言性能較差。該步槍使用300 BLK口徑。"

