msgstr "M16的第一代型號。在越南戰爭中作為M14的替代品引入，此步槍存在諸多機械故障，總體而言性能較差。此為使用300 BLK口徑的民用復刻版。"

#: .\gun\300blk.json
msgid ""
"The first generation of the M16. Introduced in vietnam as a replacement for "
"the m14 this rifle suffered from many mechanical failures and was over all a"
" very poor weapon. This rifle is chambered in 300 blackout and has an a2 "
"lower receiver giving it burst fire capabilities instead of full-auto."
msgstr ""
"M16的第一代型號。在越南戰爭中作為M14的替代品引入，此步槍存在諸多機械故障，總體而言性能較差。該步槍使用300 "
