#: .\gun\308.json
msgid "IA2 DMR"
msgid_plural "IA2 DMRs"
msgstr[0] "IA2精確射手步槍"

#: .\gun\308.json
msgid ""
"The IA2 is a select fire assault rifle designed to replace the aging FALs, "
"M16 A2s, and HK33s that are in service with the brazilian military . It's "
"covered in picatany rails and can support a wide range of attachments. The "
"DMR variant is chambered in 7.62x51 mm, otherwise known as .308, and has a "
"17.2 inch barrel (440mm). The DMR variant accepts FAL magazines just like "
"the sniper variant."
msgstr ""
"IA2是一款可選射擊模式的突擊步槍，旨在取代巴西軍隊中老化的FAL、M16 "
"A2和HK33步槍。它全身覆蓋皮卡汀尼導軌，可支持多種附件。精確射手步槍變體使用7.62×51毫米（即.308）口徑，槍管長17.2英寸（440毫米）。與狙擊變體一樣，精確射手步槍變體可使用FAL彈匣。"

#: .\gun\308.json
msgid "IA2 sniper"
msgid_plural "IA2 snipers"
msgstr[0] "IA2狙擊步槍"

#: .\gun\308.json
msgid ""
"The IA2 sniper is a semi-automatic precision rifle designed to replace the "
"aging sniper rifles that are in service with the brazilian military . It's "
"covered in picatany rails and can support a wide range of attachments. The "
"sniper variant is chambered in 7.62x51 mm, otherwise known as .308, and has "
"a 20 inch barrel (510mm). The sniper variant accepts FAL magazines just like"
" the DMR variant."
msgstr ""
"IA2狙擊步槍是一款半自動精確步槍，旨在取代巴西軍隊中老化的狙擊步槍。它全身覆蓋皮卡汀尼導軌，可支持多種附件。狙擊變體使用7.62×51毫米（即.308）口徑，槍管長20英寸（510毫米）。與精確射手步槍變體一樣，狙擊變體可使用FAL彈匣。"

#: .\gun\308.json
msgid "RFB"
msgid_plural "RFB"
msgstr[0] "RFB"

#: .\gun\308.json
msgid ""
"The RFB� is the first truly ambidextrous 7.62 NATO bullpup ever developed, "
"thanks to its patented, forward ejecting system. It�s also one of the safest"
" bullpups ever made, with the breach separated from the shooter�s face by "
"two layers of 1.6mm steel."
msgstr ""
"RFB� 是第一款真正意義上的左右手通用 7.62 NATO "
"無託式步槍，這得益於其專利的前拋殼系統。它也是迄今為止最安全的無託式步槍之一，其槍膛通過兩層 1.6 毫米厚的鋼板與射手面部隔開。"

